data.text: Highlights: Hadleigh finished the League season with a flourish as they won by 8 wickets against Southend. The best for Southend were knocks of 68 from both P McIntosh and N Khan. Skipper Adam Fleming for Hadleigh led from the front taking 4-47 and then scoring his first century of the season finishing on 129. Paul Tibbenham reached 61* to steer Hadleigh home.
